SUMMARY:Fleece & Fiber Prep with Nelly DeVault
DESCRIPTION:Saturday\, May 9th\, 2026\, 1:00-4:00 PM \nIn this workshop we will go over scouring a raw fleece\, hand combing\, carding\, and making batts on a drum carder. \nMaterials fee of $10 will cover fleece samples. Please bring to class.\nStudents will take home their carded and combed preparations.\nStudents should bring a wheel or drop spindle if they wish to sample their samples during class. \n$55 BSWG members \n$65 Student non-BSWG members (includes one year guild membership) \n$85 non-BSWG members (includes one year guild membership) \nClass size: 3-8 \nRegister Here \n\n           Download QR
URL:https://bloomspinweave.org/event/fleece-fiber-prep-with-nelly-devault
CATEGORIES:Bloomington Spinners and Weavers Fiber Arts Guild Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bloomspinweave.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/25-5-Fiber-prep-Nelly.jpg
END:VEVENT
